|14|          │       │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |lineitem|1       |11          |
|15|          │       └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |orders  |1       |11          |
|16|          └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR        |        |1       |11          |
|17|            └─TABLE FULL SCAN            |customer|1       |11          |
=============================================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([customer.c_name], [customer.c_custkey], [orders.o_orderkey], [orders.o_orderdate], [orders.o_totalprice], [T_FUN_SUM(lineitem.l_quantity)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
